Package com.bradyrussell.tsqlparser.generated

Interface TSqlParserListener

All Superinterfaces:
org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
All Known Implementing Classes:
TSqlCommentsFromDescriptionListener, TSqlDescriptionFromCommentsListener, TSqlExtractDescriptionsListener, TSqlParserBaseListener
public interface TSqlParserListener
extends org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
This interface defines a complete listener for a parse tree produced by TSqlParser.
